                "tmpr_prtc_cn":"<p> <span data-input-buffer=\"INPUT_BUFFER_DATA;Mozilla%2F5.0%20(Windows%20NT%2010.0%3B%20Win64%3B%20x64)%20AppleWebKit%2F537.36%20(KHTML%2C%20like%20Gecko)%20Chrome%2F121.0.0.0%20Safari%2F537.36%20Edg%2F121.0.0.0;cafe.naver.com\"></span></p><p id=\"SE-a93b6651-3cd5-4848-a117-06e4f0d8e5de\" class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left se-is-text-paragraph-block-selected\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span id=\"SE-fc098e61-6132-42f0-9d01-d6306d6ce63c\" class=\"se-ff-system se-fs15 __se-node\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 16);\"><b>**장기체류 임시보호 가능하며 입양전제 우선으로 진행합니다.</b></span></p><p id=\"SE-d7a85209-3b44-4f19-bd37-5eebbf273078\" class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left se-is-text-paragraph-block-selected\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span id=\"SE-f88ec558-808f-4635-a986-5d496b4abb69\" class=\"se-ff-system se-fs15 __se-node\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 16);\"><b>단순임시보호의 경우 입양상담을 위해 입양상담이 있을 때 꼭 센터로 방문해주셔야 되며</b></span></p><p id=\"SE-4e47ffdd-5a41-4a56-9f50-127afd85da94\" class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left se-is-text-paragraph-block-selected\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span id=\"SE-b03a9466-33c0-4079-b484-05ff8c0b5b09\" class=\"se-ff-system se-fs15 __se-node\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 16);\"><b>기본 관리및 체중 관리를 꼼꼼하게 하실 수 있는 가정(반려동물 없는)이 적합합니다.</b></span></p><p> </p>",
